719034f-b.title: Manhattan: Edgecombe Avenue - 150th Street (West)
719034f-b.text:
Colonial Park: A northward view of the northern half of this Park
that lies between Edgecombe (left) and Bradhurst (right) Aves. The
photographers vantage point is near West 150th Street and shows in the
foreground a cleared space for group playing. This is a set of 3 views.
Views 1 \& 2:September 1, 1935.
View 3:-August 29, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
